parse

public static MediaType parse(String description)
Parses Media Type description to create a MediaType object. The description must take the following form: 
        media-type     = type "/" subtype *( ";" parameter )
        type           = token
        subtype        = token

Parameters:
description - The media type description (i.e. the value of a Content-Type header).
Returns:
